## SECTION 4 — SMART CONTRACT SPECIFICATION

Sourced from `CHANGELOG.md` v0.3.0: [raw.githubusercontent](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/welshDog/BROskiPets-LLM-dNFT/main/CHANGELOG.md)

### 4.1 Contract: `contracts/EEPVengers.sol`
| Parameter | Value |
|---|---|
| **Standard** | ERC-721 |
| **MAX_SUPPLY** | 78 (hardcoded) |
| **Network** | Sepolia testnet (deployment pending) |
| **Framework** | Foundry + OpenZeppelin v5 |
| **Test Coverage** | 16 Foundry tests + 10,001 fuzz runs |

### 4.2 Contract ABI — Key Functions
```solidity
// WRITE — AGENT_ROLE gated
function evolve(uint256 tokenId, string calldata newCID, string calldata newStage) external;

// READ — View functions
function evolveCooldownRemaining(uint256 tokenId) external view returns (uint256);
function totalMinted() external view returns (uint256);

// Events emitted
event PetMinted(uint256 tokenId, address owner);
event PetEvolved(uint256 tokenId, string newCID, string newStage, uint256 timestamp);
```

### 4.3 Access Control Roles (OpenZeppelin v5 AccessControl)
| Role | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE` | adminMultisig — granted in constructor |
| `MINTER_ROLE` | Granted externally post-deploy |
| `AGENT_ROLE` | Required to call `evolve()` |

### 4.4 Contract Mechanics
- **Evolution cooldown:** 1-hour between evolve calls per token
- **First evolution:** Immediately allowed (`lastEvolved == 0` bypass)
- **Security guards:** `Pausable`, `ReentrancyGuard`, `AccessControl`
- **Constructor:** Single `adminMultisig` argument — all other roles granted externally

